{
  "stem": "21582.4",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I can tell you how reassuring it was.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "At least in his love, I was safe, if, if nothing else, as isolated as I was.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it gave me tremendous comfort, for whatever it was worth in reality.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "At that time, while we were-- we had this legitimate existence, where the very few Jews and the very few Jewish streets were left, people started to build bunkers.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And if you-- the houses that we-- the buildings that we lived in were really pretty empty.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was a very ghostly-- even though there were only a few streets-- it was very ghostly.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was, you know, It was only like shadows of life that was all gone.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we knew quite well where they went.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we had a bunker too.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Now, there were-- in, in our bunker, that's when we met Mr.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Miodowski, Moisze Miodowski.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I mention his name because nobody heard of him, but should have.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "He had a voice that was so divine.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "He, he was in operas.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Actually he was a [HEBREW], because he was Jewish.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But he also-- I don't know if he ever performed in operas.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I'm not sure.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My father, he became-- he, he sort of-- Our family took him in.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Now, how did we get to know him?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He drifted in-- I don't know how-- back into the Warsaw Ghetto.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was with a group of Jews from his little town who were taken to a field.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they were told to dig their own graves.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And, they were-- and the people were shot, lined up and shot.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I guess to add dignity to the moment, he did what he knew how to do best and he started to sing.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he sang the [HEBREW]-- not the-- when Jewish people die, [HEBREW].",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
